    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/6349e3f0971707bec60675170730daf1.avif?t=1763357914\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras_big/6349e3f0971707bec60675170730daf1.avif?t=1763357914 width=800 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A fast-paced 2D platformer packed with action and endless challenges!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/163afc2450f3e04698c1ed8db479b13e.poster.avif?t=1763357914\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/163afc2450f3e04698c1ed8db479b13e.webm?t=1763357914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/163afc2450f3e04698c1ed8db479b13e.mp4?t=1763357914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Skeleton, and your favorite animals have mysteriously disappeared!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump, hit weird creatures, slide down ropes, and race through a world full of traps, chaos, and sudden surprises.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/4a580cdf0f860980b4ffb09fce78f850.poster.avif?t=1763357914\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/4a580cdf0f860980b4ffb09fce78f850.webm?t=1763357914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/4a580cdf0f860980b4ffb09fce78f850.mp4?t=1763357914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smash enemies, dodge deadly hazards, and don’t stop moving — every second counts in this fast-paced, hand-crafted platformer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/bddb55c14d06641a5e505e99e258e0c7.poster.avif?t=1763357914\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/bddb55c14d06641a5e505e99e258e0c7.webm?t=1763357914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/bddb55c14d06641a5e505e99e258e0c7.mp4?t=1763357914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bony Odyssey is a wild journey packed with unexpected twists, silly moments, and satisfying action. Just don’t fall into the abyss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for an adventure that never slows down?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858790/extras/9cf92bccfd2b89b63eaa643ec3a645e9.avif?t=1763357914\" width=64 height=64 /></span><br>Don't miss such fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add to wishlist!</p>",
